HEADWORD: Caligo
<hw>Ca*li"go</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
darkness.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Dimness or obscurity of sight,
dependent upon a speck on the cornea; also, the speck itself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

